{"tid":847702,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家係咪都係越大越鍾意羅宋湯？","createTime":"2018-10-04T11:06:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-04T11:22:41.000Z","uid":85235,"like":10,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ce23fb2dfdd2f73489fd89a196956db4c9911579","tid":847702,"uid":85235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T11:06:15.000Z","msg":"今日去餐廳食餐簡單嘅晚餐，當我問到是日餐湯有咩個時，佢話得返忌廉湯（唔知係南瓜定粟米）。當堂我成個食晚餐嘅mood冇曬。但我又諗返起細個都好鍾意食忌廉湯，點解而家會咁反感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n突然覺得忌廉湯就好似初戀咁，諗落好美好，粟米甜，湯嘅顏色都好純白。但味道方面比較單調，最後我地可能都厭倦左對方，無終而散。<br />\n<br />\n而羅宋湯就好似個好有經驗嘅情人咁，佢肴製咗好耐，佢識好多野，好多味，同而家嘅我好夾。<br />\n<br />\n諗到呢度碗忌廉湯嚟左，可能我太耐冇飲，我發現佢比我想像中甜，同印象中有啲出入。我繼續飲，繼續回憶返細個飲忌廉湯嘅一點一滴，然後我個湯都反常地越飲越甜。究竟係我鍾意新鮮感定係忌廉湯係我唔再飲佢嘅幾年都慢慢地進步，成長，晉升到第二個層次？我冇再深究，因為呢刻我淨係想知<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家係咪都係細個鍾意忌廉湯大個鍾意羅宋湯？？<br />\n<br />\nYes <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nNo <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"609e3089802f74ac43ce3c8a62cda5c94d0ac23f","tid":847702,"uid":150706,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T11:11:18.000Z","msg":"由細到大都係羅宋湯派"},{"pid":"d79a810725e42b73ad26f3ebedf0c8fd42ba6263","tid":847702,"uid":170595,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T11:12:18.000Z","msg":"紅湯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ddff2e45cfa32f497609624bf6a2c487b63cfb1","tid":847702,"uid":10398,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T11:13:19.000Z","msg":"淨係會飲忌廉湯<br />\n真心唔識欣賞羅宋湯 咁咸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9bc0354fb3c54bba61f72042aba8cbc5a8bf6ab","tid":847702,"uid":85235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"609e3089802f74ac43ce3c8a62cda5c94d0ac23f","tid":847702,"uid":150706,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T11:11:18.000Z","msg":"由細到大都係羅宋湯派"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T11:19:28.000Z","msg":"轉會派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知幾時會轉返忌廉<br />\n我覺得茶記羅宋湯同餐廳個啲嘅分別都幾大下<br />\n忌廉通常表現好平穩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 小中伏啲"},{"pid":"b25954c01988d1ce706c927514bd3bb1c4d19ba6","tid":847702,"uid":85235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ddff2e45cfa32f497609624bf6a2c487b63cfb1","tid":847702,"uid":10398,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T11:13:19.000Z","msg":"淨係會飲忌廉湯<br />\n真心唔識欣賞羅宋湯 咁咸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T11:20:08.000Z","msg":"啲菜同肉都係賣點嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdb776612884bc09661832739ffdf8371696027c","tid":847702,"uid":43008,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T11:22:41.000Z","msg":"我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}